#! -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

_DISPLAY_SPECTRUM - Display FTS-2 spectrum

=head1 SYNOPSIS

_DISPLAY_SPECTRUM_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive displays FTS-2 data.

It is based on the original _FTS_DR_ primitive.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

=head1 EXTERNAL TASKS

The following external tasks are used:

